K09D0044-2_H0094-2:220a-21: pa'i mdzod ces bya ba ste /
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:220b-0: @220b de la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' ni /
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:220b-1: mi zad pa'i mdzod bcu rab tu 'thob bo //

K09D0044-2_H0094-2:220b-8: la 'jug pa'i gter mi zad pa'i mdzod rab tu
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:220b-9: 'thob bo // de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:220b-10: chos bstan pa yongs su bzung zhing chud mi zos
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:220b-11: par bya ba'i phyir dran pas bzung ba'i gter mi
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:220b-12: zad pa'i mdzod rab tu 'thob bo //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:220b-13: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi chos kyi tshul
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:220b-14: dang dgongs pa shin tu bstan pa la mkhas par
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:220b-15: bya ba'i phyir blo gros rnam par nges pa'i gter
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:220b-16: mi zad pa'i mdzod rab tu 'thob bo //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:220b-17: chos kyi tshul rnam par dbye ba la mkhas par
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:220b-18: bya ba'i phyir rigs pas 'dzin pa'i gter mi zad
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:220b-20: nam mkha'i dbyings dang mnyam pa'i blos dus gsum thams
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:220b-21: cad khyab par bya ba'i phyir blo tshad med pa'i

K09D0044-2_H0094-2:221a-7: byang chub sems dpa' spyod pa rgyun mi 'chad pas
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:221a-8: thams cad mkhyen pa nyid chags pa med pa'i thabs

K09D0044-2_H0094-2:221a-13: gyis sangs rgyas kyi byin gyi rlabs kyis phyogs bcur
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:221a-15: de'i tshe tshigs su bcad pa 'di dag smras so //

K09D0044-2_H0094-2:221a-24: dus gsum rgyal ba ji snyed bzhugs pa yi //

K09D0044-2_H0094-2:221b-6: zhing gi yon tan bsngags pa zad mi 'gyur //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:221b-7: 'di 'dra'i zhing rnams thams cad ma lus par //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:221b-8: mi yi mchog gis ji snyed mthong gyur pa //

K09D0044-2_H0094-2:221b-14: zhing gi phyogs rnams rab tu rgyas par byed //

K09D0044-2_H0094-2:221b-16: de dag dpe byad bzang pos lus kyang mdzes //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:221b-17: de dag mtha' yas yang dag so so shes //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:221b-18: 'gro ba'i rgya mtsho mi zad ji bzhin no //

K09D0044-2_H0094-2:221b-23: 'di 'dra'i zhing rnams ma lus bzung byas te //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:221b-24: nyan thos spyod yul dag la dad med pa //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:221b-25: rang rgyal thams cad shin tu spangs gyur te //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:221b-26: mi yi dam pas shin tu gang gyur cig /
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:221b-27: de dag de 'dra'i yongs bsngo sems ldan pa //

K09D0044-2_H0094-2:222a-6: dpal ldan mthu can gzhan gyis pham mi nus //

K09D0044-2_H0094-2:222a-8: de dag smon lam mthu stobs yangs pa yin; ;yongs su bsngo ba chags pa med gyur cing //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:222a-9: bsod nams zad med de dag mdzod du zhugs //

K09D0044-2_H0094-2:222b-23: 'gro ba rkyen 'byung chos kyang rab tu shes //

K09D0044-2_H0094-2:222b-25: thams cad 'jig par byed pa gang yang med //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:222b-26: de dag las dang las min rab tu shes //

K09D0044-2_H0094-2:358b-15: chos nyid mtshan nyid rjes su shes byas shing //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:358b-16: bsam yas mtshan nyid de dag mthong gyur nas //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:358b-17: mtshan nyid med pa'i shes la rmongs pa med //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:358b-18: de ltar zab pa'i spyod pa rab brtson pa //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:358b-19: de dag byang chub rtag par brtson pa ste //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:358b-20: de dag smon lam de yang rtog pa med //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:358b-21: 'gro ba kun gyi don du de dag brtson //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:358b-22: de dag 'jig rten rnams las 'das gyur cing //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:358b-23: 'chi 'pho yongs su rtog pa med byas te; ;sprul pa 'dra bar sems kyang rig byas nas //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:358b-24: de dag 'gro ba gdul phyir rab tu 'jug /
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:358b-25: de dag mthong dang dran pa 'di 'dra ste //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:358b-26: las kyi smin pas 'jig rten byung ba yi //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:359a-1: gsum pa yi sems can thams cad la //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:359a-2: de dag yongs su bskyab par mngon par brtson //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:359a-3: 'gro ba kun gyi 'du shes rgyu ba dang //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:359a-4: rnam par rtog pa ji snyed tha dad pa'i //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:359a-5: skal ba mi mnyam de dag de bzhin shes //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:359a-6: ngo bo nyid las nam yang phyir mi ldog /
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:359a-7: shes pas mkhas pa chos rab bsngags pa rnams //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:359a-8: 'gro ba kun la snying brtse'i sems ldan pas //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:359a-9: chos kyi tshul la rjes su sems byed cing //
K09D0044-2_H0094-2:359a-10: tshul mkhas de dag de ltar yongs su bsngo //
